queryLines: SELECT Screen_1 AS Stage1, Screen_2 AS Stage2, Screen_3 AS Stage3, Screen_4 AS Stage4, Screen_5 AS Stage5, SUM(Devices) AS Total_Devices FROM hpx_first_use_behavior_flow WHERE Date >= '2023-05-01' AND Screen_2 != 'welcome_S2' AND Screen_3 != 'welcome_S3' AND Screen_4 != 'welcome_S4' AND Screen_5 != 'welcome_S5' GROUP BY Screen_1, Screen_2, Screen_3, Screen_4, Screen_5 ORDER BY Total_Devices DESC
